{"tid":630284,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"全能到仆街！小C朗攞神射手獎","createTime":"2018-04-15T13:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T16:14:48.000Z","uid":20634,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"acbab39ab9765139e9c4ece2e873f6f7d45edf32","tid":630284,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T13:08:04.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=ZwCjmBT0kzfAd9fKNb%2F40whMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=29774867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】雖然皇家馬德里球星基斯坦奴朗拿度今季能否贏得西甲神射手獎仍屬未知之數，不過其兒子小C朗就率先贏得學校的神射手獎，這亦是他首個獎項，認真威水。<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，皇馬球星基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）是一名神射手，其職業生涯已累積超過600個入球，而其年僅7歲的兒子小C朗就盡得C朗真傳，憑着他精湛的球技，周六就贏得了一個特別的獎盃，那就是學校的神射手獎，並在祖母Dolores Aveiro陪同下領取他首個獎盃和獎牌。<br />\n<br />\n祖母Dolores Aveiro當然十分自豪，更將她和孫兒捧起獎盃的合照放在Instagram ，與大家分享喜悅，而數小時後， C朗亦轉載了這張相片到他的Instagram ，公開恭喜他的兒子首次贏得足球獎項，並在圖片說明上寫上，「小C朗是學校的神射手！恭喜你，兒子！」<br />\n<br />\n馬拉加VS皇家馬德里<br />\nNow632台16/04 02:45直播<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : Twitter圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/7/427/21077573427/21082966461_600x402.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F7%2F427%2F21077573427%2F21082966461_600x402.jpg&h=1d61fd73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9be3f7a786e73fbd6c00f1536640d49cfed127ec","tid":630284,"uid":54373,"like":36,"dislike":31,"score":5,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T13:08:34.000Z","msg":"又點，無老母的可憐虫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efcc801fa2b88e7f0c1f477bf233d50b27c2a713","tid":630284,"uid":20634,"like":12,"dislike":11,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T13:08:36.000Z","msg":"自己攞唔到，個仔攞到，都算一種安慰既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d753d679b50d3181022ad7adbd3b5db42239ff","tid":630284,"uid":46526,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"rep